"it's growing", F.F.

00:10:34.635 --> 00:10:37.506 position:21% line:83% align:start
The body is actually
being transformed into this.

00:10:37.539 --> 00:10:39.373 position:30% line:83% align:start
I may not able
to simply rip these off.

00:10:39.406 --> 00:10:42.209 position:24% line:83% align:start
-Jolyne, any pain?
-[exhales]

00:10:43.210 --> 00:10:44.912 position:35% line:89% align:start
No. But...

00:10:44.945 --> 00:10:47.616 position:7% line:83% align:start
This is still bad news, because
it means I touched that bone.

00:10:47.648 --> 00:10:50.351 position:33% line:83% align:start
What's more,
since I'm turning floral,

00:10:50.384 --> 00:10:51.986 position:13% line:83% align:start
you'd better stay far away
from me.

00:10:52.720 --> 00:10:54.221 position:10% line:89% align:start
You might get infected, also.

00:10:56.190 --> 00:10:56.824 position:35% line:89% align:start
[grunts]

00:10:59.260 --> 00:10:59.827 position:35% line:89% align:start
[F.F.] Ugh!

00:11:00.595 --> 00:11:01.630 position:19% line:89% align:start
This is simply a plant.

00:11:01.662 --> 00:11:04.965 position:13% line:83% align:start
There's nothing more to it
than that.

00:11:04.999 --> 00:11:06.834 position:10% line:89% align:start
I don't know what kind it is,

00:11:06.867 --> 00:11:08.869 position:33% line:83% align:start
but I do know
that instead of blood

